	   <tr><td colspan=2>well dude im not sure that i know how to get to erudin city libary but i can certainly tell you how to get to highhold keep.<br>The first thing u need to do is get a tp to WC.<br>Then run to the right wall where the derv camps are follow that wall with the wall on your right as going to the opposite side. At the wend of the wall u will come to a zone which is Kithicor Forest.You must be very careful passinf through here. Do not pass kithicor between 7pm and 7am u must start that part of the journey at around 8am to 6am because the undead spawn at night.<br>Once u zone into kithicor keep along the right wall this will take a while so get a sow if possible. The first zone you come to is a whole in the wall which leads to another zone which hits misty thinket if i reember correctly carry on past that and u will come to another open zone turn right and go through the zone.<br><br>When u enter highpass then you will be a little hit for this but the orcs agro and 3 could kill you at your level. Run through the first part and under the tunnel carry on to the top and u will see a left turn. turn left up here and cross the bridge where there is a guard on the way there are also some highpass citizens who will defend you from the orcs but the citizes are weak and conned whit to me at 22 although they agro<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
